{"id": 2032, "genre": 1000, "title": "你如今能在互联网上找到哪些新型友谊？", "description": "仔细想想，似乎也发展了一些新朋友。", "record_count": 6896, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171124151429S1QiIRtYTFrb9UPe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-26T17:00:10Z", "questions": [{"id": 3340, "title": "你如今能在互联网上找到哪些新型友谊？", "content": "你如今能在互联网上找到哪些新型友谊？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 250866, "content": "点赞之交，朋友圈常点赞的也没几个人，点成了脸熟，关系感觉近了很多", "image": "img/option/option/201711241515174p6XHZzfAb9gwC1O.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250867, "content": "留言之交，互相动态门儿清的捧场王，关系不知不觉就变好了", "image": "img/option/option/20171124151605h6xJET1yWGVtbH9v.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250870, "content": "艾特之交，看到有好玩的就艾特我去看，就表示有把这份友谊放心上", "image": "img/option/option/201711241517014EzJYsfmgUG9NFe0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250871, "content": "段友之交，一起在段子下留言二次创作，看段子发弹幕能笑到一块", "image": "img/option/option/20171124151727mUuBL7l15Qy6ZkoF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250872, "content": "转发之交，转发我的状态或经常和我转发相同文章，简直是三观契合伴侣", "image": "img/option/option/20171124151921dM5CNRQxEjWrylG4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250873, "content": "谢邀之交，有问题就邀请他来答，他提出问题怎么都要回上几句", "image": "img/option/option/20171124152005UIYte0Vjsryua9zM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250874, "content": "小世界之交，哎呀，看你转发，你也喜欢这个作家/歌者/艺术家/这幅画啊！", "image": "img/option/option/20171124152117CgQ9Hpd0JTth8VUj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250875, "content": "+1之交，XX那边安利来的，只有我是这样吗？还有我，+1，握手", "image": "img/option/option/20171124152150pi1jhr4lZVRgzuW7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}